= SDL_RendererFlip =
An enumeration of flags that can be used in the flip parameter for [[SDL_RenderCopyEx]].


== Values ==
{|
|SDL_FLIP_NONE
|do not flip
|-
|SDL_FLIP_HORIZONTAL
|flip horizontally
|-
|SDL_FLIP_VERTICAL
|flip vertically
|}


